Feline2::
In leopard form, she was picked up and carried off by HotRod. "Who 
was that bot?" She winced as his hand touched the wound on her torso.

KitKat::
She kissed Drillbit and then looked at Apocolypse.  She looked back 
at Drillbit. "When this meeting with my new associate is complete, I 
will wish to speak to you, alone." She smiled at him and gave him a 
wink.  She knew that he would know what what she meant.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, RoboRick007 <rfa007@h...> wrote:
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> "Thanks, Magnus!"
> He swooped Feline into his arms.(OOC: Hope you dont mind Logo.)
> He started running off. He wanted to put some distance between them 
and
> there attackers before taking time to transform.
> "Come on Magnus!"
> 
> ::DrillBit::
> 
> He took her in his arms.
> "I'm fine. How about you?" He said to KitKat.
> He then gave her a long kiss.
